yingyinNormal.en: I create life! And I destroy it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我创造了生命。然后再毁掉它。

yingyinNormal.en: We configured Jarvis' matrix, to create something new.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们以贾维斯为基质，创造了一个新事物。

yingyinNormal.en: Men of peace create engines of war. Invaders create avengers. People create smaller people, children.
yingyinNormal.zh: 和平人士创造了战争机器，侵略者创造了复仇者，人类创造了更小的人类，孩子。

yingyinNormal.en: Stay with me. We don't create shit. We don't build anything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 注意听，我们屁都创造不出来，我们造不出任何东西。

yingyinNormal.en: You are here to create history and influence what is to come. I don't think I can do it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是来创造历史并影响未来的。我觉得我做不到。

yingyinNormal.en: Arnold gave you that early on. Do you remember the desire to create something of lasting beauty?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是以前阿诺德给你的，你还记得创造永恒之美的欲望吗？

yingyinNormal.en: This is freedom to create, and to do, and to build, as artists, as individuals.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一种有关创造、做事、建造的自由，是一门艺术，是一种独立的精神气质。

yingyinNormal.en: Humans didn't create them, but we can use them to foster our own evolution and achieve our goals.
yingyinNormal.zh: 法则不是人类创造，但我们可以利用法则培养进步，达到目标。

yingyinNormal.en: So to avoid the misery of unemployment, the government should instead spend money to create jobs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此为了避免失业带来的伤痛，政府增加支出来创造工作机会。

yingyinNormal.en: You create the world of the dream. We bring the subject into that dream, and they fill it with their subconscious.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你创造梦空间，我们将目标带进来，令其迁移意识到此。

yingyinNormal.en: It gave them the key they needed to create weapons that could adapt to any mutant power.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这给予了哨兵计划所需的关键，这也让他们创造出可以复制任何变种人技能的哨兵。

yingyinNormal.en: We create and perceive our world simultaneously. And our mind does this so well that we don't even know it's happening.
yingyinNormal.zh: 同时创造和认知我们的精神世界。过程如此畅顺 令人毫不知情。

yingyinNormal.en: We help merchants to grow, create jobs, and open new markets in ways that were never before possible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们帮助这些小生意人成长，创造出前所未有的工作机会，开拓出崭新的市场。

yingyinNormal.en: To create a Wormhole based on real science, Visual Effects supervisor Paul Franklin turned to Kip Thorne.
yingyinNormal.zh: 基于真正的科学创造一个虫洞，视觉特效总监保罗富兰克林求助于基普索恩。

yingyinNormal.en: He wasn't interested in the appearance of intellect or wit. He wanted the real thing. He wanted to create consciousness.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他对智慧或才智的表现并不感兴趣，他想要真实的东西，他想创造意识。

yingyinNormal.en: But if you don't help me cook, I'm gonna take bunch of those hot dogs and create an new appetizer called Pigs In Ross.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是如果你不帮我，我会用一堆热狗创造出一道新的开胃菜叫“罗斯猪肉卷”。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm proud that we ignite innovation, create jobs, benefit customers and help entrepreneurs fulfill their dreams.
yingyinNormal.zh: 让我感到更自豪的是，我们能够点燃创新，创造机会，造福客户，并且能给创业者圆梦。

yingyinNormal.en: Thor? You helped create this? I've had a vision. A whirlpool that sucks in all hope of life and at its center is that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 托尔？你帮着创造了这个？我看见了幻象，在吞噬一切生之希望的漩涡中心，是这个东西。

yingyinNormal.en: The way she turned Sam into Owen. Put it all together, and you got a system to create the perfect undercover operative.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她就是这样把萨姆变成欧文的，把一切综合起来，你就有了一个创造完美卧底特工的系统。

yingyinNormal.en: There's our justice, the kind men create. We base it on things like the Ten Commandments. But those can be read a million different ways.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的正义是先辈创造的以《十诫》之类的戒律为基础，但文字总有不同的解读方法。
